text:
Ok, the app itself is fine - not bad at all (ie better than the stock iphone email app); 
Udated the app - nothing really better/much different (besides google annoyingly pushing its Meet more and more to try to bite off Zoom marketshare; note - thx for at least allowing to turn off that stupid footer bar with meet that just took extra space) but it started freezing (early may 2021)... Also, why is there the copy / paste issue?? This issue has been happening on this app for like a few years and does not change with updates - in fact, this issue started happening after an update a couple years ago and all future updates really did not improve much - maybe only slightly cosmetically better UI.. 
pls fix the copy / paste issue - ie you cannot easily scroll and select text in an email...
